column2: "You came, ARKS."
"You came, you monsters."
"We really didn't think you could escape from that."
"Yup. Thanks to you, our stomach is completely empty. It feels weird and makes funny noises."
"That's the first time we've suffered like that."
"That's the first time we've been frustrated like that."
"What's wrong? You're kinda quiet."
"Yeah, you're quiet. Did you get scared?"
"Did you lose your will to fight? Do you not feel like fighting anymore?"
"I wonder why... I feel like I've been through this situation before."
"I feel like I remember what to say in times like this... it's strange."
"I didn't come here to fight... I came here to kill you."
"Hm. Interesting. Those words are very interesting."
"You're right, good thing we waited. Those are the most interesting words we've heard since we were born."
"Then, let's do it."
"Yep yep."

"No hard feelings, whoever wins!
A fight between monsters!
Let's begin!"
"[Double]"
"Quest progress has been saved."
